Name: project_priority_weight
Description: Weight assigned to project priority ranking

Name: team_allocation_count
Description: Number of teams assigned to a project

Name: worker_load_percentage
Description: Percentage of full-time equivalent assigned to sprint

Name: sprint_length_days
Description: Number of days in a sprint

Name: task_priority_rank
Description: Priority rank of a task within sprint

Name: feature_estimated_effort
Description: Estimated effort for a feature (in story points)

Name: blocker_resolution_time
Description: Expected days to resolve a blocker

Name: velocity_prediction
Description: Forecasted velocity for next sprint (story points)

Name: meeting_duration_minutes
Description: Duration of Scrum event in minutes

Name: feature_inclusion_flag
Description: Whether a feature is included in next release
